{"tid":765461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一到夜晚就會聽下歌檢視自己","createTime":"2018-08-02T18:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T18:59:47.000Z","uid":89134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b60c0b3378c0dcded18b937af818302f35c23f99","tid":765461,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:20:30.000Z","msg":"讀書同玩運動有少少天份 但半途而廢 的起心肝發力又發現同人距離好遠，想發展新興趣又發現起步俾人慢最後放棄（天才兒童1985）。感情失敗（有多少愛可以重來），真心朋友寥寥可數（最佳損友），最後發現自己虛度緊光陰（陀飛輪），搵唔到生存意義。"},{"pid":"5f584f10598e103aaf98618f5eddd13ade01da74","tid":765461,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:29:35.000Z","msg":"想幫你含"},{"pid":"bbae69df202fc67229b7c7623aef9804c28418b5","tid":765461,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:32:36.000Z","msg":"陀飛輪好似唔係虛渡光陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7c1e6e55343a5f7ecfd34240aa6ddf3ee9d11f","tid":765461,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbae69df202fc67229b7c7623aef9804c28418b5","tid":765461,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:32:36.000Z","msg":"陀飛輪好似唔係虛渡光陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:41:28.000Z","msg":"大概係冇好好利用同把握以前既時間 放係更有意義既地方做咗啲冇意義既事 以為自己好威 到頭來浪費青春<br />\n每首歌唔同人理解都有唔同偏差<br />\n對我嚟講就係咁 當然首歌既原意對我都有好大提醒"},{"pid":"17594ba78e8e42d54c119744af3aba52a43749c6","tid":765461,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f584f10598e103aaf98618f5eddd13ade01da74","tid":765461,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:29:35.000Z","msg":"想幫你含"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:41:44.000Z","msg":"大家咁話"},{"pid":"dbc8fbeac207fe9e0480335809b0a2a3f54ff800","tid":765461,"uid":182479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"曖昧 還不如聽首情歌的機會 忘了誰"},{"pid":"b6e3e4af796f49d1e89ab55378dc71340b